body:
🌻🍃 Moomin Aesthetic Music Playlist 🍃🌻

You like Moomin? You like the Moomin Aesthetic? You want some bops that make you feel like a mythical being in the woods?

Well today is your lucky day my paw-footed creature friend.

This has some sad songs, some happy ones, some calming, and some exciting. But overall has the vibe of the beloved universe of Moominvalley.

If there are any songs you personally dont think fit or ones you would add to the playlist yourself let me know! I’d like anyone’s input 😊
